Our Logo
Home State Lissajous
Our Motto
Gem√ºtlichkeit
The Home State Lissajous (pronounced, lee-sa-zjhoo) is one of many striking patterns formed by a Foucault pendulum. The sweeping motion changes based on the geographic coordinates of the pendulum as well as the time of day and year.
Yes, we are nerds.
For us at Home State, our Lissajous represents a specific place and time as well as the journey through the winding paths, peaks and valleys of everyday life.
In this way, the lissajous represents the marriage of art and science, location and time, a memory, and a dream.
Wherever you are, wherever you‚Äôre going, you can always find your way to a Home State of mind.
At Home State, our slogan is ‚ÄúGem√ºtlichkeit‚Äù - a German word that captures the heart of what we strive to create every day. It speaks to a feeling of warmth, coziness , friendliness, and good cheer -- like gathering with good people in a space that feels like Home.
